Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:02.75,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a penetratingly precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.68,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Once he gets started, you can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.68,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Today, we visit a five-story pagoda\Ndeep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.83,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Its legendary power leads to an impossible crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:10.44,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:12.35,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.05,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}His name? Detective Conan!
